  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1012437">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1012437/" class="title-link">复习王小波</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1012437"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/luzhong/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1043570-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/luzhong/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">临渊羡鱼</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2005-11-27"
      class="main-meta">2005-11-27 17:08:11</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1012437_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  王小波是个有趣的人。他的文有趣和深刻。就我而言，他的杂文让我读后就沉默了。该说的让他说完了，想说的一时还不能以语言组织起来。  这本书由李银河选编，汇聚了王的名篇，很多文章的题目已经成为一种“成语”。我想大体体现了王的主要思想。“一个自由主义者”“浪漫骑士”...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1012437_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1012437_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





